                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r"/>-115r: Funeral Ritual, መጽሐፈ፡ ግንዘት፡. Published more than once: መጽሐፈ፡ ግንዘት።  (Roma, 1908). The prayers include the names of actual departed people, written in red ink. F<locus target="#36rv"/> (in small text) contains instructions in Amharic.</summary>
